    "text": "Kagema are male prostitutes. Kagema regularly pass for Kabuki actors, but offer sexual services to both men and women through Kagema teahouses. Kagema often charge a premium compared to Yūjo and regularly service clients of a higher social standing. Kagema present as one of three types: \"Yarō\" or young man who presents in a masculine manner; \"Wakashū\" or adolescent boy who presents in a sweeter, more innocent form of masculinity; and \"Onnagata\" or feminine boy, who presents as strongly feminine to the point of passing as a young woman.",
