   },
   {
    "text": "Yūkaku are legal red-light districts, where both brothels and prostitutes recognised by the Japanese government operated. Okiya gather Yujo, women of pleasure, and Kagemajaya gather Kagema, young men of pleasure. Oiran, high-class prostitutes, can frequent these districts if not servicing a client. Geishas are often found in okiyas as well and served more as surrogate wives for wealthy men.",
